    dc:title "Crinoid-associated shrimps of the genus Laomenes A. H. Clark, 1919 (Caridea: Palaemonidae: Pontoniinae): new species and probable diversity" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185051>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185022>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185044>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185043>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185046>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185047>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185029>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185045>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185038>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185052> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185051>
    dc:description "FIGURE 33. Coloration of Laomenes ceratophthalmus (Borradaile, 1915) (A, C, E) and Laomenes nudirostris (Bruce, 1978) (B, D, F). A – D, ovigerous females. E, F, males." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185051/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185022>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Laomenes amboinensis (De Man, 1888), ovigerous female. A, B, distal part of carapace and rostrum. C, eyes. D, antennule. E, same, distolateral margin of basal antennular segment. F, antenna. Scale 1 mm; E, without scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185022/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185044>
    dc:description "FIGURE 26. Laomenes ceratophthalmus (Borradaile, 1915), ovigerous female. A, B, distal part of carapace and rostrum. C, eyes. D, antenna. E, F, same, distolateral margin of basal antennular segment. G, antenna. H, epistomial horns. I, telson. J, distolateral margin of uropodal exopod. Scale 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185044/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185043>
    dc:description "FIGURE 25. Laomenes ceratophthalmus (Borradaile, 1915). A, ovigerous female, B, male. Scale 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185043/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185046>
    dc:description "FIGURE 28. Laomenes ceratophthalmus (Borradaile, 1915), ovigerous female. A, B, mandible. C, same, distal margin of incisor process. D, maxillule. E, maxilla. F, maxilliped I. G, maxilliped II. H, maxilliped III. I, oral appendages and thoratic sternite III. Scale 1 mm; C, I, without scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185046/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185047>
    dc:description "FIGURE 29. Laomenes ceratophthalmus (Borradaile, 1915), ovigerous female (A – I), male (J). A, pereiopod I. B, same, chela. C, pereiopod II. D, E, same, carpus. F, same, fingers. G, pereiopod III. H, same, distal margin of propodus and dactylus. I, endopod of pleopod I. J, appendix masculina. Scale 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185047/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185029>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Laomenes clarki sp. nov., ovigerous female. A, B, distal part of carapace and rostrum. C, eyes. D, E, antennule. F, same, distolateral margin of basal antennular segment. G, antenna. H, epistomial horns. I, thoratic sternites. Scale 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185029/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185045>
    dc:description "FIGURE 27. Laomenes ceratophthalmus (Borradaile, 1915), juvenile (pcl. 3 mm) (A, B), juvenile (pcl. 6 mm) (C, D), juvenile (pcl. 11 mm) (E). A – E, distal part of carapace and rostrum. Scale 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185045/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185038>
    dc:description "FIGURE 20. Laomenes tigris sp. nov., ovigerous female (A – E), male (F, G). A, B, F, G, distal part of carapace and rostrum. C, distal part of carapace. D, eyes. Scale 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185038/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185052>
    dc:description "FIGURE 34. Crinoid hosts of the representatives of the genus Laomenes A. H. Clark. A, Himerometra robustipinna (Carpenter, 1881) (Himerometridae). B, Amphimetra tesselata (Müller, 1841) (Himerometridae). C, Oxycomanthus benetti (Müller, 1841) (Comasteridae). D, F, Comantheria (Comanthus) briareus (Bell, 1882) (Comasteridae). E, Zygometra punctata A. H. Clark, 1912 (Zygometridae)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185052/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

